- `/Users/dhamidi/projects/tclc/CLAUDE.md` - Project instructions and working process

From the git status, I can see the most recent work involves:
- Namespace export and import commands (commit aa8eeb9)
- Namespace command resolution (commit 666e19a)
- Unified command storage with :: prefix (commit 12b555d)

2. I should use grep, glob, and read tools efficiently
